Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
A Curve must have an associated metric. As an example, here we use Kerr \
spacetime.\
\>", "Item",ExpressionUUID->"fc8a780f-088e-490a-87aa-b2dfa3be8e8c"],

